commit_message:
Add Introduction and Documentation tabs; drop "X" support

Adds table explaining degenerate base symbols.

(“X” is not recommended by Comnish-Bowden, so dropping for now)

Add favicon

From https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/dna_1327514

Converted transparent background to white with Image Magick and
instructions from https://stackoverflow.com/a/28534287/1712389:

$ convert dna.png -background white -alpha remove -flatten -alpha off
dna-white.png

Converted 512x512 PNG to ICO file with http://faviconit.com/en.

Also removed mention of trackers since it looks like Privacy Badger
detects some potential trackers from Twitter and CDNJS Cloudfare
domains (probably innocent enough).
